<plot>A Hard Day's Work's first episode follows Chibrowski and his crew for a day at Versa Corp. The leader of the team, Chibrowski, decides they will devote their work day to getting Monday off of work. But the task is not without its obstacles; new employees, an evil boss, and a ticking punch card clock stand between them and freedom. What transpires will push the boundaries rational human conduct.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?011365</url></doc>
